quran[339]{c,v,t}:
  25,21,Jo log hamare huzoor pesh honay ka andesha nahin rakhte woh kehte hain “kyun na Farishte hamare paas bheje jayein? Ya phir hum apne Rubb ko dekhein? Bada ghamand le baithey yeh apne nafs mein aur hadd se guzar gaye yeh apni sarkashi mein
  25,22,"Jis roz yeh Farishton ko dekhenge woh mujreemo ke liye kisi basharat (khush khabri) ka din na hoga, cheekh uthenge ke panaah-ba-khuda"
  25,23,Aur jo kuch bhi inka kiya dhara hai usey lekar hum gubaar(dust) ki tarah uda dengey
  25,24,Bas wahi log jo jannat ke mustahiq hain us din acchi jagaah thehrenge aur dopahar (mid-day) guzarne ko umdah muqaam payenge
  25,25,Aasmaan ko cheerta hua ek baadal us roz namudaar hoga aur Farishton ke parey ke parey (rank after rank) utaar diye jayenge
  25,26,Us roz haqeeqi baadshahi sirf rehman ki hogi aur woh munkireen ke liye bada sakht din hoga
  25,27,Zaalim Insaan apna haath chabayega aur kahega “kaash maine Rasool ka saath diya hota
  25,28,"Haaye meri kambakhti, kaash maine falaan shaks ko dost na banaya hota"
  25,29,Uske behkaye mein aakar maine woh naseehat na maani jo mere paas aayi thi. Shaytaan insaan ke haqq mein bada hi bewafa nikla”
  25,30,"Aur Rasool kahega ke “Aey mere Rubb, meri qaum ke logon ne is Quran ko nishana tadheek bana liya tha (the object of their ridicule)”"
  25,31,"(Aey Muhammad), humne to isi taraah mujreemo ko har Nabi ka dushman banaya hai , aur tumhare liye tumhara Rubb hi rehnumayi aur madad ko kaafi hai"
  25,32,"Munkireen kehte hain “is shaks par saara Quran ek hi waqt mein kyun na utaar diya gaya? Haan, aisa is liye kiya gaya hai ke isko achhi tarah hum tumhare zehan nasheen karte rahein aur (isi garaz ke liye) humne isko ek khaas tarteeb ke saath alag alag ajzaa ki shakal di hai"
  25,33,"Aur (ismein yeh maslihat bhi hai) ke jab kabhi woh tumhare samne koi nirali baat (ya ajeeb sawal) lekar aaye, uska theek jawaab bar waqt humne tumhein de diya aur behtareen tareeqe se baat khol di"
  25,34,Jo log aundhey mooh jahannum ki taraf dhakele janey waley hain unka mauquf bahut bura (most erroneous) aur unki raah hadd darjah galat hai
  25,35,Humne Moosa ko kitaab di aur uske saath uske bhai Haroon ko madadgaar ke taur par lagaya
  25,36,Aur unse kaha ke jao us qaum ki taraf jisne hamari aayat ko jhutla diya hai. Aakhir e kaar un logon ko humne tabaah karke rakh diya
  25,37,"Yahi haal qaum e Nooh ka hua jab unhon ne Rasoolon ki takzeeb ki, humne unko garq (drown/duba) kardiya aur duniya bhar ke logon ke liye ek nishaan e ibrat bana diya, aur in zaalimon ke liye ek dardnaak azaab humne muhaiyya kar rakkha hai"
  25,38,Isi tarah Aad aur Samood aur ashaab e Rass aur beech ki sadiyon ke bahut se log tabaah kiye gaye
  25,39,"Aur un mein se har ek ko humne ( pehle tabaah honay walon ki) misalein dey dey kar samjhaya, aur aakhir e kaar har ek ko gaarat (destroy) kardiya"
  25,40,Aur us basti par to inka guzar ho chuka hai jispar badhtareen baarish barsayi gayi thi.Kya inhon ne uska haal dekha na hoga? Magar yeh maut ke baad dusri zindagi ki tawakku hi nahin rakhte
  25,41,"Yeh log jab tumhein dekhte hain to tumhara mazaaq bana lete hain, (Kehte hain) “kya yeh shaks hai jisey khuda ne Rasool bana kar bheja hai"
  25,42,"Isne to humein gumraah karke apne maboodon se bargashta(astray/behka/gumrah) hi kardiya hota agar hum unki aqeedat par jam na gaye hotey”. Accha, woh waqt door nahin hai jab azaab dekh kar inhein khud maloom ho jayega ke kaun gumraahi mein door nikal gaya tha"
  25,43,Kabhi tumne us shaks ke haal par gaur kiya hai jisne apni khwahish e nafs ko apna khuda bana liya ho? Kya tum aisey shaks ko raah e raast par laney ka zimma le sakte ho
  25,44,"Kya tum samajhte ho ke inmein se aksar log sunte aur samajhte hain? Yeh to jaanwaron ki tarah hain, balke unse bhi gaye guzre"
  25,45,Tumne dekha nahin ke tumhara Rubb kis tarah saaya phayla deta hai? Agar woh chahta to usey daimi (constant) bana deta. Humne Suraj ko uspar daleel (sun its pilot) banaya
  25,46,Phir (jaisey jaisey Suraj utha jaata hai) hum is saaye ko rafta rafta apni taraf sameit-te chale jatey hain
  25,47,"Aur woh Allah hi hai jisne raat ko tumhare liye libaas, aur neend ko sukoon e maut, aur din ko jee uthne ka waqt banaya"
  25,48,Aur wahi hai jo apni rehmat ke aagey aagey hawaon ko basharat bana kar bhejta hai phir aasmaan se paak pani nazil karta hai
  25,49,Taa-ke ek murda ilake ko iske zariye zindagi bakshe aur apni makhlooq mein se bahut se jaanwaron aur Insano ko sairaab (quench thirst) karey
  25,50,Is karishme ko hum baar baar inke saamne latey hain taa-ke woh kuch sabaq lein. Magar aksar log kufr aur nashukri ke siwa koi dusra rawaiyya ikhtiyar karne se inkar kardete hain
  25,51,Agar hum chahte to ek ek basti mein ek ek nazeer (darr sunane waala) utha khada karte
  25,52,"Pas (aey Nabi) , ka firon ki baat hargiz na maano aur is Quran ko lekar inke saath jihad-e-kabeer karo"
  25,53,"Aur wahi hai jisne do samandaron ko mila rakkha hai, ek lazeez o shereen(sweet) , dusra talkh o shur (bitter and saltish), aur dono ke darmiyan ek purda hayal hai, ek rukawat hai(insurmountable barrier) jo unhein gud-mud honay se roakey huey hai"
  25,54,"Aur wahi hai jisne pani se ek bashar (Insaan) paida kiya, phir ussey nasab aur susraal (by blood and by marriage) ke do alag silsile chalaye .Tera Rubb bada hi qudrat wala hai"
  25,55,"Is khuda ko chodh kar log unko poojh rahey hain jo na inko nafaa pahuncha sakte hain na nuqsaan, aur upar se mazeed yeh ke kafir apne Rubb ke muqablay mein har baagi ka madadgaar bana hua hai"
  25,56,"(Aey Muhammad), tumko to humne bas ek mubashir (khush khabri dene waala) aur nazeer (darr sunane wala) bana kar bheja hai"
  25,57,"Insey kehdo ke “ main is kaam par tumse koi ujrat (recompense) nahin maangta, meri ujrat bas yahi hai ke jiska jee chahe woh apne Rubb ka raasta ikhtiyar karle”"
  25,58,"Aur (aey Muhammad) us khuda par bharosa rakkho jo zinda hai aur kabhi marne waala nahin, uski hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo,apne bandon ke gunaahon se bas usi ka ba-khabar hona kaafi hai"
  25,59,"Woh jisne chey (six) dino mein zameen aur aasmaano ko aur un saari cheezon ko bana kar rakh diya jo aasmaan o zameen ke darmiyaan hain, phir aap hi (qayinaat ke takht e sultanat) ‘Arsh’ par jalwa farma hua. Rehman, uski shaan bas kisi jaanne waley se pucho"
  25,60,In logon se jab kaha jata hai ke is Rehman ko sajda karo to kehte hain “Rehman kya hota hai? Kya bas jisey tu kehde usi ko hum sajda karte phirein?” yeh dawat inki nafrat mein ulta aur izafa kardeti hai
  25,61,Bada mutabarrak(ba-barakat) hai woh jisne aasmaan mein burj (fortified spheres) banaye aur us mein ek chiraag aur ek chamakta Chand roshan kiya
  25,62,"Wahi hai jisne raat aur din ko ek dusre ka jaanasheen banaya, har us shaks ke liye jo sabaq lena chahe, ya shukar guzaar hona chahe"
  25,63,Rehman ke (asli) banday woh hai jo zameen par narm chaal chalte hain aur jaahil unke mooh ko aayein to keh detay hain ke tumko salaam
  25,64,Jo apne Rubb ke huzur sajde aur qayaam mein raatein guzarte hain
  25,65,"Jo duaein karte hain ke “Aey hamare Rubb, jahannum ke azaab se humko bacha le, uska azaab to jaan ka laagu hai"
  25,66,Woh to bada hi mustaqar(evil abode) aur muqaam hai”
  25,67,"Jo kharch karte hain to na fizool kharchi karte hain na bukhl, balke unka kharch dono intehaaon (extremes) ke darmiyan aitadaal par qayam rehta hai"
  25,68,"Jo Allah ke siwa kisi aur mabood ko nahin pukarte, Allah ki haraam ki hui kisi jaan ko na-haqq halaak nahin karte, aur na zina (adultery) ke murtakib hotay hain. Yeh kaam jo koi karey woh apne gunaah ka badla payega"
  25,69,Qayamat ke roz usko mukarrar azaab diya jayega aur isi mein woh hamesha zillat ke saath pada rahega
  25,70,"Illa yeh ke koi (in gunaahon ke baad) toubah kar chuka ho aur iman laa kar amal e saleeh karne laga ho, aisey logon ki buraiyon ko Allah bhalaiyon se badal dega aur woh bada gafoor o raheem hai"
  25,71,Jo shaks toubah karke neik amali ikhtiyar karta hai woh to Allah ki taraf palat aata hai jaisa ke palatne ka haqq hai
  25,72,(Aur Rehman ke bandey woh hain) jo jhoot ke gawaah nahin bante aur kisi lagv (fizul/vain) cheez par unka guzar ho jaye to shareef aadmiyon ki tarah guzar jatey hain
  25,73,Jinhein agar unke Rubb ki aayat suna kar naseehat ki jati hai to woh uspar andhey aur behre bankar nahin reh jatey
  25,74,"Jo duaein maanga karte hain ke, “Aey hamare Rubb, humein apni biwiyon aur apni aulaad se aankhon ki thandak de, aur humko parheizgaaron ka imam bana.”"
  25,75,"Yeh hain woh log jo apne sabr ka phal manzil-e-buland ki shakal mein payenge, aadaab o tasleemaat se unka istaqbaal hoga"
  25,76,Woh hamesha hamesha wahan rahenge. Kya hi accha hai woh mustaqar (excellent abode) aur woh muqaam
  25,77,"(Aey Muhammad), logon se kaho, “mere Rubb ko tumhari kya haajat padi hai agar tum usko na pukaro. Ab ke tumne jhutla diya hai, anqareeb woh saza paogey ke jaan chudhani muhaal (never be able to avoid) hogi”"
  26,1,Taa seen Meem
  26,2,Yeh kitaab e Mubeen ki aayat hain
  26,3,"(Aey Muhammad), shayad tum is gham (grief) mein apni jaan kho dogey ke yeh log iman nahin latey"
  26,4,Hum chahein to aasmaan se aisi nishani nazil kar sakte hain ke inki gardanein iske aagey jhuk jayein
  26,5,In logon ke paas rehman ki taraf se jo nayi naseehat bhi aati hai yeh ussey mooh moad letey hain
  26,6,"Ab ke yeh jhutla chuke hain, ankareeb inko is cheez ki haqeeqat (mukhtalif tareeqon se) maloom ho jayegi jiska yeh mazaak udatay rahey hain"
  26,7,Aur kya inhon ne kabhi zameen par nigaah nahin daali ke humne kitni kaseer miqdaar mein har tarah ki umdah nabataat(vegetation) ismein paida ki hain
  26,8,"Yaqeenen ismein ek nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar maanne waley nahin"
  26,9,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,10,Inhein us waqt ka qissa sunao jabke tumhare Rubb ne Moosa ko pukara “ zaalim qaum ke paas jaa
  26,11,"Firoun ki qaum ke paas, kya woh nahin darte?”"
  26,12,"Usne arz kiya “aey Rubb, mujhey khauf hai ke woh mujhey jhutla dengey"
  26,13,"Mera seena ghutt-ta hai aur meri zubaan nahin chalti, aap Haroon ki taraf risalat bhejein"
  26,14,"Aur mujhpar unke haan ek jurm ka ilzam bhi hai, is liye main darta hoon ke woh mujhey qatal kar dengey”"
  26,15,"Farmaya “hargiz nahin, tum dono jao hamari nishaniyan lekar, hum tumhare saath sab kuch suntey rahenge"
  26,16,"Firoun ke paas jao aur ussey kaho, humko Rubb ul aalameen ne isliye bheja hai"
  26,17,Ke tu bani Israel ko hamare saath janey de”
  26,18,Firoun ne kaha “kya humne tujhko apne haan baccha sa nahin paala tha? Tu nay apni umar ke kai saal hamare haan guzare
  26,19,"Aur iske baad kar gaya jo kuch ke kar gaya, tu bada ehsan faramosh aadmi hai”"
  26,20,Moosa ne jawab diya “us waqt woh kaam maine nadanishtagi (inadvertently) mein kardiya tha
  26,21,Phir main tumhare khauf se bhaag gaya. Iske baad mere Rubb ne mujhko hukum ata kiya aur mujhey Rasoolon mein shamil farma liya
  26,22,Raha tera ehsan jo tu nay mujhpar jataya hai to iski haqeeqat yeh hai ke tu nay bani Israel ko ghulaam bana liya tha”
  26,23,Firoun ne kaha “aur yeh Rubb-ul-Aalameen kya hota hai?”
  26,24,"Moosa ne jawab diya “Aasmano aur zameen ka Rubb, aur un sab cheezon ka Rubb jo aasmaan o zameen ke darmiyan hain, agar tum yaqeen laney waley ho.”"
  26,25,Firoun ne apne gird o pesh ke logon se kaha ‘Sunte ho?”
  26,26,"Moosa ne kaha, “tumhara Rubb bhi aur tumhare un aabaa o ajdaad ka Rubb bhi jo guzar chuke hain”"
  26,27,"Firoun ne ( haazirin se) kaha “ tumhare yeh Rasool sahib jo tumhari taraf bhejey gaye hain, bilkul hi pagal maloom hotay hain”"
  26,28,"Moosa ne kaha “mashriq o magrib aur jo kuch inke darmiyan hai sabka Rubb, agar aap log kuch aqal rakhte hain”"
  26,29,Firoun ne kaha “ agar tu nay mere siwa kisi aur ko mabood maana to tujhey main un logon mein shamil kardunga jo qaid khano mein paday saddh(rotting) rahey hain”
  26,30,Moosa ne kaha “Agarche main le aaon tere saamne ek sareeh cheez bhi?”
  26,31,Firoun ne kaha “Accha to le aa agar tu saccha hai”
  26,32,(Uski zubaan se yeh baat nikalte hi) Moosa ne apna asa (staff) phenka aur yakayak woh ek sareeh azdha (serpant/snake) tha
  26,33,Phir usne apna hath (bagal se) khincha aur wo sab dekne walon ke saamne chamak raha tha
  26,34,Firoun apne gird o pesh ke sardaron se bola “yeh shaks yaqeenan ek maahir jaadugar hai
  26,35,"Chahta hai ke apne jaadu ke zoar se tumko tumhare mulk se nikal de, ab tum batao tum kya hukum dete ho?”"
  26,36,Unhon ne kaha “ isey aur iske bhai ko rok lijiye aur shehron mein harkare (heralds) bhej dijiye
  26,37,Ke har siyane jaadugar ko aapke paas le aayein”
  26,38,Chunanchey ek roz muqarrar waqt par jaadugar ikatthey karliye gaye
  26,39,Aur logon se kaha gaya “tum ijtima mein chaloge
  26,40,Shayad ke hum jaadugaron ke deen hi par reh jayein agar woh gaalib rahey”
  26,41,Jab jaadugar maidan mein aa gaye to unhon ne Firoun se kaha “humein inaam to milega agar hum gaalib rahey?”
  26,42,"Usne kaha “ haan, aur tum to us waqt muqarrabeen (nearest to me) mein shamil ho jaogey”"
  26,43,Moosa ne kaha “ phenko jo tumhein phenkna hai”
  26,44,Unhon ne fawran apni rassiyan aur laathiyan phenk di aur bole “ Firoun ke iqbal se hum hi gaalib rahenge.”
  26,45,Phir Moosa ne apna asa (staff) phenka to yakayak woh unke jhootey karishmon ko hadap karta chala ja raha tha
  26,46,Ispar sarey jaadugar be-ikhtiyar sajde mein gir paday
  26,47,Aur bol uthey ke “ maan gaye hum Rubb-ul-Aalameen ko
  26,48,Moosa aur Haroon ke Rubb ko”
  26,49,"Firoun ne kaha “tum Moosa ki baat maan gaye qabl iske ke main tumhein ijazat deta! Zaroor yeh tumhara bada hai jisne tumhein jaadu sikhaya hai. Accha, abhi tumhein maloom hua jaata hai, main tumhare haath paon mukhalif simton (opposite sides) mein katwaunga aur tum sabko sooli (crucify) chadha dunga”"
  26,50,"Unhon ne jawab diya “kuch parwah nahin, hum apne Rubb ke huzur pahunch jayenge"
  26,51,Aur humein tawaqqu hai ke hamara Rubb hamare gunaah maaf kardega kyunke sabse pehle hum iman laye hain”
  26,52,"Humne Moosa ko wahee (revelation) bhejhi ke “raat o raat mere bandon ko lekar nikal jao, tumhara peecha kiya jayega”"
  26,53,Ispar Firoun ne (Faujein jama karne ke liye) shehron mein naqeeb (heralds) bhej diye
  26,54,(aur kehla bheja) ke “yeh kuch mutthi bhar log hain
  26,55,Aur inhon ne humko bahut naraaz kiya hai
  26,56,Aur hum ek aisi jamaat hain jiska shewa har waqt chokanna rehna hai”
  26,57,Is tarah hum unhein unke baaghon aur chashmon (water –springs)
  26,58,Aur khazano aur unki behtareen qayam-gaahon se nikal laaye
  26,59,Yeh to hua unke saath aur (dusri taraf) bani Israel ko humne in sab cheezon ka waris kardiya
  26,60,Subah hotey hi yeh log unke taaqub (pursuit) mein chal paday
  26,61,Jab dono girohon ka aamna saamna hua to Moosa ke saathi cheekh utthey ke “ hum to pakde gaye”
  26,62,"Moosa ne kaha “ hargiz nahin mere saath mera Rubb hai, woh zaroor meri rehnumayi farmayega”"
  26,63,Humne Moosa ko wahee ke zariye se hukum diya ke “maar apna asa (staff) samandar par” yakayak samandar pahtt gaya aur uska har tukda ek azeem o shaan pahad ki tarah ho gaya
  26,64,Usi jagah hum dusre giroh ko bhi kareeb le aaye
  26,65,Moosa aur un sab logon ko jo uske saath thay humne bacha liya
  26,66,Aur dusron ko garq (duba/drown) kardiya
  26,67,"Is waqiye mein ek nishani hai, magar in logon mein se aksar manney waley nahin hain"
  26,68,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,69,Aur inhein Ibrahim ka qissa sunao
  26,70,Jabke usne apne baap aur apni qaum se pucha tha ke “yeh kya cheezein hain jinko tum poojhte ho?”
  26,71,Unhon ne jawab diya “ kuch buth (idols/murtiyan) hain jinki hum pooja karte hain aur inhi ki sewa mein hum lagey rehte hain”
  26,72,Usne pucha “kya yeh tumhari sunte hain jab tum inhein pukarte ho
  26,73,Ya yeh tumhein kuch nafaa ya nuqsaan pahunchate hain?”
  26,74,"Unhon ne jawab diya “ nahin , balke humne apne baap dada ko aisa hi karte paya hai”"
  26,75,Ispar Ibrahim ne kaha “ kabhi tumne (aankhein khol kar) un cheezon ko dekha bhi jinki bandagi tum
  26,76,Aur tumhare pichle baap dada baja latey rahey
  26,77,"Mere to yeh sab dushman hain, bajuz ek Rubb ul aalameen ke"
  26,78,"Jisne mujhey paida kiya, phir wahi meri rehnumayi farmata hai"
  26,79,Jo mujhey khilata aur pilata hai
  26,80,Aur jab main bimar ho jaata hoon to wahi mujhey shifa deta hai
  26,81,Jo mujhey maut dega aur phir dobara mujhko zindagi bakshega
  26,82,Aur jissey main umeed rakhta hoon ke roz e jaza mein woh meri khata maaf farmadega”
  26,83,"(iske baad Ibrahim ne dua ki) “Aey mere Rubb, mujhey hukum ata kar aur mujhko salihon (neik logon) ke saath mila"
  26,84,Aur baad ke aane walon mein mujhko sacchi naamwari ata kar
  26,85,Aur mujhey jannat e naeem ke warison (inheritors) mein shamil farma
  26,86,Aur mere baap ko maaf karde ke beshak woh gumraah logon mein se hai
  26,87,Aur mujhey us din ruswa na kar jabke sab log zinda karke uthaye jayenge
  26,88,Jabke na maal koi faiyda dega na Aulad
  26,89,Bajuz iske ke koi shaks qalb-e-saleem (sound heart) liye huey Allah ke huzur haazir ho”
  26,90,(Us roz) jannat parheizgaaron ke qareeb le aayi jayegi
  26,91,Aur dozakh behke huey logon ke saamne khol di jayegi
  26,92,Aur unsey pucha jayega ke “ab kahan hai woh jinki tum khuda ko chodh kar ibadat karte thay
  26,93,Kya woh tumhari kuch madad kar rahey hain ya khud apna bachao kar sakte hain?”
  26,94,Phir woh mabood aur yeh behke huey log
  26,95,Aur Iblis ke lashkar sabke sab ismein upar taley dhakeil diye jayenge
  26,96,Wahan yeh sab aapas mein jhagdenge aur yeh behke huey log (apne maboodon se) kahenge
  26,97,"Ke “khuda ki kasam , hum to sareeh gumraahi mein mubtala thay"
  26,98,Jabke tumko Rubb ul Aalameen ki barabari ka darja de rahey thay
  26,99,Aur woh mujrim log hi thay jinhon ne humko is gumraahi mein dala
  26,100,Ab na hamara koi sifarishi hai
  26,101,Aur na koi jigri dost
  26,102,Kaash humein ek dafa phir palatne ka mauqa mil jaye to hum momin hon”
  26,103,"Yaqeenan is mein ek badi nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar log iman laney waley nahin"
  26,104,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,105,Qaum e Nooh ne Rasoolon ko jhutlaya
  26,106,Yaad karo jabke unke bhai Nooh ne unsey kaha tha “kya tum darte nahin ho
  26,107,Main tumhare liye ek amaanat daar Rasool hoon
  26,108,Lihaza tum Allah se daro aur meri itaat karo
  26,109,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul Aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,110,Pas tum Allah se daro aur ( be khatke) meri itaat karo”
  26,111,Unhon ne jawab diya “kya hum tujhey maan lein halaanke teri pairwi razil-tareen (lowest/meanest) logon ne ikhtiyar ki hai?”
  26,112,Nooh ne kaha “main kya jaanu ke unke amal kaise hain
  26,113,"Unka hisaab to mere Rubb ke zimme hai, kaash tum kuch shaoor se kaam lo"
  26,114,Mera yeh kaam nahin hai ke jo iman layein unko main dhutkaar doon
  26,115,Main to bas ek saaf saaf mutanabbeh (warn) kardene wala aadmi hoon”
  26,116,"Unhon ne kaha “Aey Nooh , agar tu baaz na aaya to phitkarey huey logon mein shamil hokar rahega”"
