  26,180,"Main is kaam par tumse kisi ajar ka talib nahin hoon, mera ajar to Rabbul aalameen ke zimme hai"
  26,181,Paimane theek bharo (Give full measure) aur kisi ko ghaata (less) na do
  26,182,Saheeh tarazu se tolo
  26,183,"Aur logon ko unki cheezein kam na do, zameen mein fasaad na phaylate phiro"
  26,184,Aur us zaat ka khauff karo jisne tumhein aur guzishta nasalon ko paida kiya hai.”
  26,185,Unhon ne kaha “tu mehaz ek sehar zadah(affected by magic) aadmi hai
  26,186,"Aur tu kuch nahin magar ek Insaan hum hi jaisa, aur hum to tujhey bilkul jhoota samajhte hain"
  26,187,Agar tu saccha hai to humpar aasmaan ka koi tukda gira de”
  26,188,Shoaib ne kaha “ mera Rubb jaanta hai jo kuch tum kar rahey ho”
  26,189,"Unhon ne usey jhutla diya, aakhir-e-kaar chatri waley din (Day of Canopy) ka azaab unpar aa gaya, aur woh baday hi khauf-naak din ka azaab tha"
  26,190,"Yaqeenan ismein ek nishani hai, magar in mein se aksar log maanne waley nahin"
  26,191,Aur haqeeqat yeh hai ke tera Rubb zabardast bhi hai aur raheem bhi
  26,192,Yeh Rabbul Aalameen ki nazil karda cheez hai
  26,193,Isey lekar tere dil par amanat-daar rooh utri hai
  26,194,Taa-ke tu un logon mein shamil ho jo (khuda ki taraf se khalq-e-khuda ko) mutanabbeh (warn) karne waley hain
  26,195,Saaf saaf arabi zubaan mein
  26,196,Aur agley logo ki kitaabon mein bhi yeh maujood hai
  26,197,Kya in (ehle Makkah) ke liye yeh koi nishani nahin hai ke isey ulema-e-bani Israel jaante hain
  26,198,(Lekin inki hatdarmi ka haal yeh hai ke) agar hum isey kisi ajami (non-arab) par bhi nazil kar detey
  26,199,Aur yeh (faseeh arabi kalaam) woh inko padh kar sunata tab bhi yeh maan kar na detey
  26,200,Isi tarah humne is (zikr) ko mujrimon ke dilon mein guzara hai
  26,201,Woh ispar iman nahin latey jab tak azaab e aleem na dekh lein
  26,202,Phir jab woh be-khabari mein unpar aa padta hai
  26,203,Us waqt kehte hain “ke kya ab humein kuch mohalat mil sakti hai?”
  26,204,To kya yeh log hamare azab ke liye jaldi macha rahey hain
  26,205,"Tumne kuch gaur kiya , agar hum inhein barason tak aish karne ki mohalat bhi de dein"
  26,206,Aur phir wahi cheez unpar aa jaye jissey inhein daraya jaa raha hai
  26,207,To woh saamaan-e-zeist (provisions of life) jo unko mila hua hai inke kis kaam aayega
  26,208,(Dekho) humne kabhi kisi basti ko iske bagair halaak nahin kiya ke uske liye khabardar karne waley haqq e naseehat ada karne ko maujood thay
  26,209,Aur hum zaalim na thay
  26,210,Is (kitaab e mubeen) ko shayateen lekar nahin utray hain
  26,211,"Na yeh kaam unko sajta hai, aur na woh aisa kar hi sakte hain"
  26,212,Woh to iski samaat (hearing) tak se door rakkhey gaye hain
  26,213,"Pas (aey Muhammad), Allah ke saath kisi dusre mabood ko na pukaro, warna tum bhi saza paaney walon mein shamil ho jaogey"
  26,214,Apne qareeb-tareen rishtedaaron ko darao
  26,215,Aur iman laney walon mein se jo log tumhari pairwi ikhtiyar karein unke saath tawazo (humble/kindness) se pesh aao
  26,216,Lekin agar woh tumhari nafarmaani karein to unsey kehdo ke jo kuch tum karte ho ussey main bari-uz-zimma (not responsible) hoon
  26,217,Aur us zabardast aur raheem par tawakkul(bharosa) karo
  26,218,Jo tumhein us waqt dekh raha hota hai jab tum uthte ho
  26,219,Aur sajda guzaar logon mein tumhari naqal o harakat par nigaah rakhta hai
  26,220,Woh sab kuch sunnay aur jaanne wala hai
  26,221,"Logon, kya main tumhein bataon ke shayateen kis par utra karte hain"
  26,222,"Woh har chaal saaz, badhkaar par utra karte hain"
  26,223,"Suni sunayi baatein kaano mein phoonkte hain, aur unmein se aksar jhootey hotay hain"
  26,224,"Rahey shuaraa (poets), to unke peechey behke huey log chala karte hain"
  26,225,Kya tum dekhte nahin ho ke woh har waadi (valley) mein bhatakte hain
  26,226,Aur aisi baatein kehte hain jo karte nahin hain
  26,227,"Bajuz un logon ke jo iman laye aur jinhon ne neik amal kiye aur Allah ko kasrat se yaad kiya aur jab unpar zulm kiya gaya to sirf badla le liye, aur zulm karne walon ko anqareeb maloom ho jayega ke woh kis anjaam se do-chaar hotay hain"
  27,1,Taa Seen. yeh aayat hain Quran aur kitaab e mubeen ki
  27,2,Hidayat aur basharat un iman laney walon ke liye
  27,3,"Jo namaz qayam karte aur zakat detey hain, aur phir woh aisey log hain jo aakhirat par poora yaqeen rakhte hain"
  27,4,"Haqeeqat yeh hai ke jo log aakhirat ko nahin maante unke liye humne unke kartooton ko khushnuma bana diya hai, isliye woh bhatakte phir rahey hain"
  27,5,Yeh woh log hain jinke liye buri saza hai aur aakhirat mein yahi sabse zyada khasare (nuksaan) mein rehne waley hain
  27,6,Aur (aey Muhammad) bila shubah tum yeh Quran ek hakeem o aleem (All-wise and All-knowing) hasti ki taraf se paa rahey ho
  27,7,"(Inhein us waqt ka qissa sunao) jab Moosa ne apne ghar walon se kaha ke “mujhey ek aag si nazar aayi hai, main abhi ya to wahan se koi khabar lekar aata hoon ya koi angara chun laata hoon taa-ke tum log garam ho sako”"
  27,8,"Wahan jo pahuncha to nidaa (awaaz/pukaar) aayi ke “mubarak hai woh jo is aag mein hai aur jo iske maahol mein hai, paak hai Allah sab jahanon ka parwardigar"
  27,9,"Aey Moosa, yeh main hoon Allah, zabardast aur daana(All-Wise)"
  27,10,"Aur phenk tu zara apni laathi.” Junhi ke Moosa ne dekha laathi saanp(snake) ki tarah bal kha rahi hai to peeth phair kar bhaaga aur peechey mudh kar bhi na dekha. “Aey Moosa, daro nahin, mere huzur Rasool dara nahin karte"
  27,11,Illa yeh ke kisi ne kasoor kiya ho. Phir agar burayi ke baad usne bhalayi se apne fail (amal) ko badal liya to main maaf karne wala meharbaan hoon
  27,12,"Aur zara apna haath apne girebaan mein to daalo chamakta hua niklega bagair kisi takleef ke, yeh (dono nishaniyan) naw (nine) nishaniyon mein se hain Firoun aur uske qaum ki taraf (le janey ke liye), woh baday badh-kirdaar(wicked) log hain”"
  27,13,Magar jab hamari khuli khuli nihsaniyan un logon ke samney aayi to unhon ne kaha yeh to khula jaadu hai
  27,14,"Unhon ne sara-sar zulm aur guroor ki raah se in nishaniyon ka inkar kiya, halaanke dil unke qayel (convinced) ho chuke thay. Ab dekhlo ke un mufsidon ka anjaam kaisa hua"
  27,15,(Dusri taraf) humne Dawood o Sulaiman ko ilm ata kiya aur unhon ne kaha ke shukar hai us khuda ka jisne humko apne bahut se momin bandon par fazilat ata ki
  27,16,"Aur Dawood ka waris sulaiman hua aur usne kaha “logon, humein parindon (birds) ki boliyan sikhayi gayi hain aur humein har tarah ki cheezein di gayi hain, beshak yeh (Allah ka) numaya fazl hai.”"
  27,17,Sulaiman ke liye Jinn aur Insano aur parindon ke lashkar jama kiye gaye thay aur woh puray zabt (strict discipline) mein rakkhey jatey thay
  27,18,"Ek martaba woh unke saath kooch (marching) kar raha tha) yahan tak ke jab yeh sab chuntiyon (ants) ki waadi(valley) mein pahunchey to ek chunti (ant) ne kaha “ Aey chunityon , Apne bilon (holes) mein ghuss jao, kahin aisa na ho ke Sulaiman aur uske lashkar tumhein kuchal daalein aur unhein khabar bhi na ho”"
  27,19,"Sulaiman uski baat par muskurate huey hass pada aur bola “aey mere Rubb mujhey qaabu mein rakh ke main tere us ehsan ka shukar ada karta rahoon jo tu-nay mujhpar aur mere walidain par kiya hai aur aisa amal e saleh karoon jo tujhey pasand aaye, aur apni rehmat se mujhko apne saleh bandon mein daakhil kar.”"
  27,20,(Ek aur mauqe par) Sulaiman ne parindon ka jaiza liya aur kaha “ kya baat hai ke main falaan hud-hud (hoopoe bird) ko nahin dekh raha hoon. Kya woh kahin gayab ho gaya hai
  27,21,"Main usey sakht saza dunga, ya zubaa kardunga, warna usey mere saamne maaqool wajah pesh karni hogi"
  27,22,Kuch zyada dair na guzri thi ke usne aakar kaha “maine woh maalumaat haasil ki hai jo aapke ilam mein nahin hain. Main Saba ke mutaalik yaqeeni ittila lekar aaya hoon
  27,23,Maine wahan ek aurat dekhi jo us qaum ki hukmaran hai. Usko har tarah ka saaz o samaan baksha gaya hai aur uska takht (throne) bada azeem o shaan hai
  27,24,"Maine dekha hai ke woh aur uski qaum Allah ke bajaye Suraj ke aagey sajda karti hai” Shaytaan ne unke aamaal unke liye khushnuma bana diye aur unhein shahraah se rok diya, is waja se woh yeh seedha raasta nahin paatey"
  27,25,Ke us khuda ko sajda karein jo aasmano aur zameen ki posheeda(hidden) cheezein nikalta hai aur woh sab kuch jaanta hai jisey tum log chupate ho aur zaahir karte ho
  27,26,"Allah, ke jiske siwa koi mustahiq e Ibadat(worthy of worship) nahin, jo arsh e azeem ka maalik hai"
  27,27,Sulaiman ne kaha “abhi hum dekhe letay hain ke tu nay sach kaha hai ye tu jhoot bolne walon mein se hai
  27,28,"Mera yeh khat (letter) le ja aur usey un logon ki taraf daal de, phir alag hatt kar dekh ke woh kya radd-e-amal zaahir karte hain”"
  27,29,"Malika boli “aey ehle darbaar, meri taraf ek bada eham khat phenka gaya hai"
  27,30,Woh Sulaiman ki janib se hai aur Allah rehman o raheem ke naam se shuru kiya gaya hai
  27,31,Mazmoon yeh hai ke “ mere muqable mein sarkashi na karo aur muslim ho kar mere paas haazir ho jao”
  27,32,(khat sunakar) Malika ne kaha “aey sardaran e qaum mere is maamle mein mujhey mashwara do. Main kisi maamle ka faisla tumhare bagair nahin karti hoon”
  27,33,"Unhon ne jawab diya “hum taqatwar aur ladne waley log hain, aagey faisla aap ke haath mein hai, aap khud dekh lein ke aapko kya hukum dena hai”"
  27,34,"Malika ne kaha ke “Baadshah jab kisi mulk mein ghus aate hain to usey kharab aur uske izzat walon ko zaleel kar detay hain, yahi kuch woh kiya karte hain"
  27,35,"Main in logon ki taraf ek hadiya(gift) bhejti hoon, phir dekhti hoon ke mere elchi (envoy) kya jawaab lekar palat-te hain”"
  27,36,"Jab woh [Malika ka safeer(envoy)] Sulaiman ke haan pahuncha to usne kaha, “ kya tum log maal se meri madad karna chahte ho? Jo kuch khuda ne mujhey de rakkha hai woh issey bahut zyada hai jo tumhein diya hai. Tumhara hadiya (gifts) tumhi ko mubarak rahey"
  27,37,"aey safeer (envoy)]wapas jaa apne bhejne walon ki taraf, hum unpar aisey lashkar lekar aayenge jinka muqabla woh na kar sakenge, aur hum unhein aisi zillat ke saath wahan se nikalenge ke woh khwar hokar reh jayenge”"
  27,38,"Sulaiman ne kaha “aey ehle darbaar, tum mein se kaun uska takht (throne) mere paas laata hai qabl iske ke woh log mutii (farmabardaar) hokar mere paas haazir hoon?”"
  27,39,Jinno mein se ek qawi (mighty) haykal ne arz kiya “ main usey haazir kardunga qabl iske ke aap apni jagah se utthein. Main iski taaqat rakhta hoon aur amaanatdaar hoon”
  27,40,"Jis shaks ke paas kitaab ka ilam tha woh bola “main aapki palakh jhapakne se pehle usey laye deta hoon”. Junhi ke Sulaiman ne woh takht apne paas rakkha hua dekha, woh pukar uttha “Yeh mere Rub ka fazal hai taa-ke woh mujhey aazmaaye ke main shukar karta hoon ya kaafir e niyamat karta hoon. Aur jo koi shukar karta hai uska shukar uske apne hi liye mufeed hai, warna koi nashukari karey to mera Rubb be-niyaz aur apni zaat mein aap buzurg hai.”"
  27,41,"Sulaiman ne kaha “anjaan tareeqe se uska takht uske saamne rakh do, dekhein woh saheeh baat tak pahunchti hai ya un logon mein se hai jo raah e raast nahin paatey.”"
  27,42,"Malika jab haazir hui to ussey kaha gaya, kya tera takht (throne) aisa hi hai? Woh kehne lagi “yeh to goya wahi hai , hum to pehle hi jaan gaye thay aur humne sar-e-itaat jhuka diya tha (ya hum muslim ho chuke thay)”"
  27,43,"Usko (iman laney se) jis cheez ne rok rakkha tha woh un maboodon ki ibadat thi jinhein woh Allah ke siwa poojhti thi, kyunke woh ek kafir qaum se thi"
  27,44,"Ussey kaha gaya ke mahal mein daakhil ho, usne jo dekha to samjhi ke pani ka hauz hai aur utarne ke liye usne apne painchey utha liye (tucked up her skirt) , Sulaiman ne kaha yeh sheeshey (glass) ka chikna farsh hai ispar woh pukar utthi “Aey mere Rubb, (aaj tak) main apne nafs par bada zulm karti rahi, aur ab maine Sulaiman ke saath Allah Rabbul aalameen ki itaat qabool karli”"
  27,45,"Aur Samood ki taraf humne unke bhai Saleh ko (yeh paigaam de kar) bheja ke Allah ki bandagi karo, to yakayak woh do mutakhasim fareeq (two wrangling) ban gaye"
  27,46,"Saleh ne kaha “aey meri qaum ke logon, bhalayi se pehle burayi ke liye kyun jaldi machate ho? Kyun nahin Allah se magfirat talab karte? Shayad ke tumpar reham farmaya jaye?”"
  27,47,Unhon ne kaha “humne to tumko aur tumhare sathiyon ko badd-shaguni ka nishaan paya hai”. Saleh ne jawab diya “tumhare neik o badd shagun ka sar rishta (good and bad omens issue) Allah ke paas hai. Asal baat yeh hai ke tum logon ki aazmaish ho rahi hai”
  27,48,Us shehar mein naw (nine) jatthey-daar (ring-leaders) thay jo mulk mein fasaad phaylatey aur koi islaah ka kaam na karte thay
  27,49,"Unhon ne aapas mein kaha “ khuda ki kasam kha kar ahad karlo ke hum Saleh aur uske ghar walon par shabkhun (secret night attack) marenge aur phir uske wali(guardian) se keh denge ke hum us khandaan ki halakat ke mauqe par maujood na thay, hum bilkul sach kehte hain"
  27,50,Yeh chaal to woh chale aur phir ek chaal humne chali jiski unhein khabar na thi
  27,51,Ab dekhlo ke unki chaal ka anjaam kya hua. Humne tabaah karke rakh diya unko aur unki poori qaum ko
  27,52,"Woh unke ghar khali padey hain us zulm ki padash mein jo woh karte thay, Is mein ek nishaan e ibrat hai un logon ke liye jo ilm rakhte hain"
  27,53,Aur bacha liya humne un logon ko jo iman laye thay aur nafarmani se parheiz karte thay
  27,54,Aur Lut ko humne bheja. Yaad karo woh waqt jab usne apni qaum se kaha “kya tum aankhon dekhte badhkari karte ho
  27,55,Kya tumhara yahi chalan hai ke auraton ko chodh kar mardon ke paas shehwat-rani (sexual desire) ke liye jatey ho? Haqeeqat yeh hai ke tumlog sakht jahalat(ignorance) ka kaam karte ho.”